title: Installation and First Look of Fedora 39
description:
The latest release of Fedora, version 39, was just released.  I'm going to do a quick installation and first look of Fedora 39 inside a virtual machine, including looking at GNOME 45 as well as the experimental 'dfn5' package manager.

REFERENCED:
► https://fedoramagazine.org/announcing-fedora-linux-39/
